if;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">2.2 During continuance of this agreement SF will be authorized to provide demonstration, service, installation, uninstallation and repair of appliance as enumerated in the </span></span></span><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Annexure &lsquo;2&rsquo;</strong></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"western\" lang=\"en-US\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Part three &ndash; Service related covenants</strong></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"western\" lang=\"en-US\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">3.1 SF shall undertake service at customer location and at work shop as per the method of service, for the appliances as specified in the </span></span></span><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Annexure &lsquo;3&rsquo;</strong></span></span></span><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"> and at service delivery standards as specified in the </span></span></span><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Annexure &lsquo;4&rsquo;</strong></span></span></span><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">, in the territory allotted to SF, irrespective of the source of purchase. SF shall also undertake regular tours of all outstation areas within SF&rsquo;s territory. 247around reserve