if;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">4.9 SF will get, at its own costs, service center office, spare parts provided by 247around, customers appliances etc. kept at service center insured against all the risks and also send to 247around a copy of the policy after every renewal.</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"western\" lang=\"en-US\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">4.10 247around may position its sales/service representative at the premises of the SF and it shall be responsibility of SF to provide necessary support and facility to the representative of 247around to function smoothly.</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"western\" lang=\"en-US\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">4.11 247around sales and services personnel shall have the right under the terms of the agreement, to visit and inspect the service center at any time without any previous information or notice to the SF. The SF will provide necessary cooperation and assistance to them for inspection and shall also provide them access to the records, documents and information. </span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"western\" lang=\"en-US\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">4.12 The Service Franchisee Employee/Personnel/Technicians/Contractors/Agents employed by SF shall have no right to relation with 247around to claim any compensation/damage/salary, etc. SF will have complete control over the conduct of his personnel with the customer of the Company. </span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"western\" lang=\"en-US\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">In case any customer has any dissatisfaction because of wrong behavior of service personnel of SF, the same should be corrected by SF on priority basis. Any repetition of such reports shall be a sufficient reason for considering termination of this contract.</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"western\" lang=\"en-US\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">4.13 If call load exceeds a particular pre-decided number then SF will provide dedicated technicians for 247around provided calls.</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"western\" lang=\"en-US\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">4.14 SF should maintain all employee/contractor/sub-contractor records who attend the services given by 247around. In no case SF will send any unknown person to customer premises for doing the job. SF will take complete responsibility of the technician in case of any wrong doing.</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"western\" lang=\"en-US\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">4.15 247around may use SF premises and engineers for branding. SF agrees to allow such branding material. 247around agrees to pay for such costs.</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"western\" lang=\"en-US\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Part five &ndash; Spares</strong></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"western\" lang=\"en-US\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">5.1 To maintain quality of the product the SF shall use quality spares supplied by that brand. In case of any loss to the product or to the customer due to defective material or spare, the SF shall be solely responsible for the same and shall be liable to compensate the Company as well as the customer for the losses incurred by the Company/the customer.</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"western\" lang=\"en-US\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">5.2 In case SF purchases spares in bulk from 247around, SF will be entitled for discount as per the prevailing policy, on the list price.</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"western\" lang=\"en-US\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">5.3 At all times SF shall maintain sufficient spares of different models for all products serviced by SF. SF will arrange for spares well in advance. </span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p lang=\"en-US\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Cambria, serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><strong>Part six &ndash; Remuneration, Penalty and Payment Terms </strong></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p lang=\"en-US\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"western\" lang=\"en-US\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">6.1 For providing Annual Maintenance Contract (AMC) services and extended warranty services to the customer 247around will pay to SF on per call basis and SF agrees to provide services as per the rates specified in the rate list in &lsquo;</span></span></span><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Annexure 5</strong></span></span></span><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">&rsquo;. </span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"western\" lang=\"en-US\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">6.2 For providing services and repairs as mentioned in &lsquo;</span></span></span><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Annexure 5</strong></span></span></span><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">&rsquo; SF agrees to collect from customers rates specified in the rate list in &lsquo;</span></span></span><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Annexure 5</strong></span></span></span><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">&rsquo; and will pass 247around royalty/commission at the end of each month for that month.</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"western\" lang=\"en-US\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">6.3 For selling AMC and Extended Warranty 247around will pay to SF sales commission as per &lsquo;</span></span></span><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Annexure 7</strong></span></span></span><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">&rsquo; and SF agrees to provide services as per </span></span></span><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>&lsquo;Annexure 7&rsquo;</strong></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p lang=\"en-US\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Cambria, serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\">6.4. 247around shall make all the payments upon the service rendered as per the agreed terms and conditions. SF will raise an invoice at the end of each month and 247around will make the payment within 30 days of the date of submission of the invoice subject to statutory deductions and other deductions as agreed between 247around and SF. Further, 247around shall have the right to adjust the applicable penalty that may be levied pursuant to </span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><strong>Annexure 4</strong></span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"> from the payments (which is payable to SF). The SF shall mandatorily mention the job card numbers while raising the invoice. </span></span></span></p>\r\n<p lang=\"en-US\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Cambria, serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\">6.5. SF agrees to pay the royalty/commission amount to 247around for all jobs where SF collected payments from customers. SF agrees to pay such amount within 30 days of the invoice being raised by 247around.</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"western\" lang=\"en-US\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Part seven &ndash;Termination</strong></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"western\" lang=\"en-US\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">7.1 Either party can terminate this agreement by giving one calendar month advance notice in writing to the other party. </span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"western\" lang=\"en-US\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">7.2 247around reserves the sole right and is entitled to terminate contract with SF at any time without any notice to the SF on any of the following GROUNDS:</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<ol type=\"a\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p lang=\"en-US\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">If the SF is found guilty of fraud or misconduct</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p lang=\"en-US\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">If the SF transfers or attempts to transfer the benefits of this agreement to any other person.</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p lang=\"en-US\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Due to any other reason which causes adverse effect on the reputation and business of the SF or 247around.</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p lang=\"en-US\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">If the SF commits breach of any of the terms and conditions of this agreement</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p lang=\"en-US\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">7.3 In case the agreement is terminated for any reason whatsoever, the SF shall be responsible to settle the customer complaints/customer equipment received at service center with the respective customer to his satisfaction. Pendency if any to be duly settled with 247around in writing.</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p lang=\"en-US\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">7.4 However, the termination of SF shall not discharge or relieve the SF from</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<ol type=\"A\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p lang=\"en-US\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"