t interest as per rules of the Company.</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"western\" lang=\"en-US\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">8.2 In case at the time of termination of agreement any amount is found due against the SF, the same shall be adjusted against the security deposit and remaining amount will be returned to the SF. </span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"western\" lang=\"en-US\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Part nine &ndash; Indemnity Clause</strong></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"western\" lang=\"en-US\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">9.1 </span></span></span><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">SF shall indemnify and undertakes to always hold harmless and keep indemnified and defend 247around, its Affiliates, associate/ group companies and their respective employees, officers, representatives, agents and directors at its cost against all actions, demands, claims, losses, damages, penalty, costs, punishments, consequences and other liabilities arising out of or as a consequence of </span></span></span><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">SF&rsquo;s improper use, negligence, unauthorized alteration or modification of any part of the product, damages of any sort either to the product or to the customer, accident, fire, theft, pilferage at SF&rsquo;s service center or at customer&rsquo;s place. In addition, SF shall also indemnify 247around against any legal action taken by any customer or appliance manufacturer company in the territory covered by SF, including any complaint before the local district forum, the main reason for the same being lack of service, improper service or delayed service and damage done to customer appliance on the part of SF which culminate in deficiency in service. </span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"western\" lang=\"en-US\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Part ten &ndash; Other terms and conditions</strong></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"western\" lang=\"en-US\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">10.1 SF shall be responsible for providing any tax related documents to 247around wherever and whenever applicable, within the prescribed/specified time. In case of failure of the SF to provide such forms to 247around, SF will be liable to compensate 247around for the losses occurred to 247around.</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"western\" lang=\"en-US\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">10.2 If any difference shall arise between the parties relating to or arising out of the terms of this agreement, no part shall be at liberty to approach court of law and all such disputes shall be referred to one arbitrator to be appointed by the 247around. The Venue of the arbitration shall be New Delhi and shall be subject to the jurisdiction of New Delhi courts only.</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"western\" lang=\"en-US\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">10.3 Force Majeure &ndash; No party hereto shall be responsible or liable to the other in any manner for failure or delay in performing its obligations under this Agreement, other than the obligations to make payments provided for hereunder, when such failure, or delay is directly or indirectly due to an act of God, Governmental or local body orders or restrictions, or any other cause or circumstances beyond the reasonable control of the party concerned, provided that upon cessation of such events such party shall thereupon promptly perform or complete the performance of its obligations hereunder. </span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"western\" lang=\"en-US\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Part eleven &ndash; Declaration by SF</strong></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"western\" lang=\"en-US\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">The SF do hereby make the following declarations:</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"western\" lang=\"en-US\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">11.1 The person who has signed and executed this agreement is fully authorized and competent to sign and execute this agreement for and on behalf of the SF.</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"western\" lang=\"en-US\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">11.2 The SF shall immediately notify in writing to the 247around at its controlling Regional Office by a Registered Mail or Speed Post of any change whatsoever in the constitution of the SF whether it is relating to the change in the partnership of the SF or otherwise as the case may be from time to time whether such changes affects this agreement or not. </span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"western\" lang=\"en-US\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">11.3 There is no pending legal or administrative actions against the SF which could adversely affect the consummation of the transactions contemplated by the agreement.</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"western\" lang=\"en-US\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Part twelve &ndash; Maintenance of accounts and other records</strong></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"western\" lang=\"en-US\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">12.1 SF shall keep and maintain such regular accounts as per established practice regarding over warranty labor charges billing, sale of spares and stock book and also records of customer c