-US\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">He / she has to inform the customer that technician will visit her in the time slot and update the status as calling done in the 247around system.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p class=\"western\" lang=\"en-US\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ol start=\"6\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p class=\"western\" lang=\"en-US\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">If customer gives a particular date time for technician visit, the same is duly noted and updated in the 247around system.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p class=\"western\" lang=\"en-US\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ol start=\"7\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p class=\"western\" lang=\"en-US\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">The printed job cards are then forwarded to supervisor for further processing. </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p lang=\"en-US\" align=\"justify\"><br /> </p>\r\n<ol start=\"8\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p class=\"western\" lang=\"en-US\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Each technician has to report to the supervisor in the morning, mark his attendance and hand over the previous day\'s call report to supervisor.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p lang=\"en-US\" align=\"justify\"><br /> </p>\r\n<ol start=\"9\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p class=\"western\" lang=\"en-US\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">The supervisor has to cross check the visit details on the job card with the route chart details and segregate the calls under various heads, pending, out of stock, cancelled unproductive). Enquiry is made on previous day calls upon parts used and the charges collected in case of chargeable calls. The cash collected is deposited with cashier against each call done in previous day.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p class=\"western\" lang=\"en-US\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ol start=\"10\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p class=\"western\" lang=\"en-US\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Supervisor allocates the calls to technicians as per their own set criterion and hand over the job sheets for the days calls to the technicians.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p class=\"western\" lang=\"en-US\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ol start=\"11\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p class=\"western\" lang=\"en-US\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">The technicians calls up the customer and commits the time slot as mentioned in the job card. They also make a rough diagnosis of the problem.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p lang=\"en-US\" align=\"justify\"><br /> </p>\r\n<ol start=\"12\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p class=\"western\" lang=\"en-US\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">The technician is supposed to maintain his tool bag with the essential tools and running functional spares.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p lang=\"en-US\" align=\"justify\"><br /> </p>\r\n<ol start=\"13\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p class=\"western\" lang=\"en-US\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Technician reaches the customer place and greets the customer.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p lang=\"en-US\" align=\"left\"><br /> </p>\r\n<ol start=\"14\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p class=\"western\" lang=\"en-US\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">He inspects the appliance and gives estimate to customer. Once customer agrees for the charges he starts the repair. If engineer has to get some spare parts he gets that the next day and completes the repair.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p lang=\"en-US\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p lang=\"en-US\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Cambria, serif;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\">For All cases assigned:</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p lang=\"en-US\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<p lang=\"en-US\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Cambria, serif;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\">SF shall establish contact with customer within 1hr of receiving the job card. If job card is received after working hours of SF then SF will contact within 1 hour of start of next working day. SF shall then update 247around system. </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p lang=\"en-US\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Cambria, serif;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\">SF shall attend the job in the time s